Q13:Update the emp_salary of employees in dept_id = 101 to 10% more if their current
salary is less than 50000.

SQL> UPDATE employee110 SET emp_salary = emp_salary * 1.10 WHERE dept_id = '101' AND emp_salary < 50000;

0 rows updated.

