Q17: Retrieve all employees' names and salaries who joined after 01-01-2020.

SQL> SELECT emp_name, emp_salary FROM employee110 WHERE emp_joindate > TO_DATE('01-01-2020', 'DD-MM-YYYY');

EMP_NAME   EMP_SALARY
-------------------------------------------------- ----------
Santhosh 55000
Shidha 54000
