Q18: Write a query to select all employees whose name starts with "J"

SQL> SELECT emp_id, emp_name, emp_salary FROM employee110 WHERE emp_name LIKE 'J%';

EMP_ID   EMP_NAME      EMP_SALARY
---------- -------------------------------------------------- ----------
7   John Cs   60000
================================================================================================================================================
Q19: Select the emp_name and emp_salary for employees whose salary is between 40000
and 60000.

SQL> SELECT emp_name, emp_salary FROM employee110 WHERE emp_salary BETWEEN 40000 AND 60000;

EMP_NAME   EMP_SALARY
-------------------------------------------------- ----------
John Cs 60000
Sandhosh 55000
Shidha 54000


